<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Successful - ProConnect</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body text-center">
        <h3 class="text-success mb-3">Payment Successful!</h3>
        <p>Dear <strong><%= userName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for hiring <strong><%= workerName %></strong> for the service <strong><%= jobTitle %></strong>.</p>
        <p><strong>Booking Date:</strong> <%= hiredAt %></p>
        <p><strong>Service Scheduled On:</strong> <%= scheduledDate %></p>
        <p><strong>Razorpay Payment ID:</strong> <%= orderID %></p>
        <hr>
        <p>We appreciate your trust in <strong>ProConnect</strong> and look forward to serving you again.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
